reviewText: The filming is poor, it looks like a home movie at times and the sound is not good. But being a Colosseum fan I am glad I got it. If you are a Colosseum fan it is well worth it, if not pass on it.

Dick Heckstall- Smith is amazing. Likewise Hiseman,Clempson and Farlow! Greensade&Reeves,Mark Clark and even Barbara Thompson on flute I always loved these guys. Some spotty sound and video at times;but overall pretty good live concert film and there is not a lot that I know of!
